<P>
   BURT-REYNOLDS _ JUPITER, Fla. _ So this is what it's come to:
Photo of Burt and then-Gov. Bob Graham. $5. Burt and a guy in an
ascot. $5. Burt and the pope. $50. Burt and Loni. Both smiling.
$10. Burt ``and an older gentleman,'' said auctioneer Jay Sugarman.
``That's Groucho Marx,'' offered D. Cooper Getschal. $20. About 200
people attended one last performance Tuesday at the long-dead Burt
Reynolds Dinner Theater as the new owners cleaned out the closets
and offices with an auction. (O'Meilia, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
