(Hamilton, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 10.
</P>
<P>
   AUDIO-JUSTOUT _ Two new releases, aimed at a classical crossover
market, dabble in spiritual matters: ``The Prayer Cycle,''
featuring pop stars like Alanis Morissette, and the choral work
``Virgin of Guadalupe,'' featuring a San Antonio, Texas, vocal
ensemble. (Green/Dollar, Atlanta Journal-Constitution). 15.
</P>
