<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-05 11:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4938 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-NATO-EUROPE-BOS &LR;      05-05 1281
