minorities, women and young gay men has been launched by Mayor
Willie Brown. DuPont Pharmaceuticals is donating $1 million to the
effort over the next five years. The mayor says he hopes the
program will encourage other businesses to contribute a total of $5
million over the same period. By ULYSSES TORASSA.
