<DATE_TIME> 1999-05-05 13:02 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5048 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u s &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-HKN-BRUINS-ART-BOS &LR;      05-05 1202
