Game 2! 28! 25! W, 4-3 (ot)! 30! 27! L, 3-2 (ot) &QL; 
Game 3! 27! 24! L, 3-2 (ot)! 21! 18! L, 3-2 &QL; 
Game 4! 18! 15! L, 3-0! 23! 22! W, 4-1 &QL; 
Game 5! 26! 26! W, 4-0! 39! 36! W, 4-3 (2ot) &QL; 
Game 6! 33! 30! L, 3-2 (ot)! 31! 31! W, 2-0 &QL; 
Totals! 159! 145! 2-4! 163! 153! 4-2 &QL; 
 &QL; 
