   TORNADO-MIDWEST CITY &QL;
</P>
<P>
   MIDWEST CITY, Okla _ Midwest City, a densely populated Oklahoma
City suburb and home of Tinker Air Force Base, took it in the gut
Monday. Reports say that at least one home, and the family of four
that inhabited it, are completely gone, swept away by the killer
tornado. By JENNIFER AUTREY. Story will move in ``a'' general news
category. &QL; 
