<P>
   MACYS-SPINOFF (Los Angeles) _ Tapping into one of the hottest
areas in retailing, Macy's is spinning off a new chain of
free-standing stores specializing in beauty products, candles and
other ``impulse'' merchandise _ and using a local shopping center
as its Southern California testing ground. By Enrique Rivero.
