   HEINZ-AD-COLUMN (Undated) _ Using its flagship condiment as a
battering ram, H.J.Heinz is in the middle of a major campaign to
revamp itself as a zippy, modern corporate behemoth, not the slow,
barely growing behemoth it has long been. By Constance L. Hays.
