5-04 --Katie Noland, 17, has the title of Advanced Teenage Miss
Majorette of the Southeast under her belt; her license plate bears
the words by which she lives, and succeeds. Baton twirling's
development has been hampered by a lack of role models, promotion
and fans. (Jennifer Podis/Palm Beach Post Photo)
</P>
<P>
