Your shampoo may be hazardous to your hair. Many women and men have
trouble with their hair. Be wary of overconditioning and using waxy
ingredients like oils and cholesterol, which weigh the hair down.
Instead, use alcohol-free styling products. (Cox News Service
Photo)
</P>
