<TEXT>
<P>
   JOKES
</P>
<P>
   Q: What does a snail say when he's riding on a horse's back?
</P>
<P>
   A: Hey, slow down! Zach Anderson.
</P>
<P>
   Q: Where do turtles live?
</P>
<P>
   A: Mobile homes. Melanie Haning.
</P>
<P>
   Q: Why were the two elephants asked to leave the beach?
</P>
<P>
   A: Because they only had one pair of trunks. Alicia Templin.
</P>
